body_html:
Try the example on the v0.12 branch.

https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/r0.12/tensorflow/examples/learn/wide_n_deep_tutorial.py

tf.TensorShape has breaking change in master branch (rename argument shape -> dense_shape. see https://groups.google.com/a/tensorflow.org/forum/?utm_medium=email&utm_source=footer#!msg/discuss/OePXmC9kJ7o/SRErOoYCDQAJ for more other API changes), and the examples catch up these changes. So examples in master branch could not work with 0.12 or older TensorFlow runtime.
